---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title='Terms of Service - 202Labs'>
  <main class='container mx-auto px-4 py-8'>
    <h1 class='text-3xl font-bold mb-6'>Terms of Service</h1>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing or using the services provided by 202Labs, you agree to be
        bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms,
        please do not use our services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>2. Description of Services</h2>
      <p>
        202Labs is a software development agency that provides custom software
        solutions, web development, mobile app development, and related
        consulting services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>3. Client Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>
        Clients are responsible for providing accurate and timely information,
        feedback, and approvals as required for the successful completion of
        projects.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
        4. Intellectual Property Rights
      </h2>
      <p>
        Unless otherwise agreed upon in writing, 202Labs retains all
        intellectual property rights to the code, designs, and other materials
        created during the course of a project. Upon full payment, clients are
        granted a non-exclusive license to use the final deliverables.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>5. Payment Terms</h2>
      <p>
        Payment terms will be outlined in the project proposal or contract.
        202Labs reserves the right to suspend services for overdue payments.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>6. Confidentiality</h2>
      <p>
        202Labs agrees to keep all client information confidential and not to
        disclose any proprietary information without prior written consent.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        202Labs shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special,
        consequential, or punitive damages resulting from the use of our
        services.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>8. Termination</h2>
      <p>
        Either party may terminate the service agreement with written notice.
        The client shall pay for all services rendered up to the termination
        date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>9. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance
        with the laws of the jurisdiction where 202Labs is registered.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='mb-8'>
      <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>10. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        202Labs reserves the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time.
        Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class='mt-8'>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
